trans-unit.source: By default, <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command> controls on a form raise validator controls on the form to perform validation when the form is submitted to the server.
trans-unit.target: Som standard <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command>i et skjema heve validerer kontroller i skjemaet til å utføre validering når skjemaet er sendt til serveren.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command>

trans-unit.source: To disable automatic validation, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command.CausesValidation%2A> property on the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command> to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Sett for å deaktivere automatisk validering av <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command.CausesValidation%2A>egenskap i den <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command>til `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Command.CausesValidation%2A>
